Domestic transactions
	693 - Foreign exchange transferred to another domestic bank
		R - Domestic receipts and payments for goods
		S - Domestic receipts and payments involving foreign currency denominated investment
		T - Domestic transfer receipts and payments
		L - Domestic receipts and payments involving foreign currency loans
		P - Domestic service receipts and payments
		Q - Domestic Carbon emission rights trading receipts and payments
		N - Other domestic transactions
